# AhaDiff

Use AhaDiff to turn AI-written diffs into verified lessons, claims, quiz cards,
and review signals.

- Run `ahadiff learn HEAD~1..HEAD` after committed changes.
- Run `ahadiff learn --staged` before committing staged work.
- Use `ahadiff verify <run_id>` before trusting generated explanations.
- Ground summaries in verified claims with file-line evidence.
- Keep API keys and local provider endpoints out of committed files.
